"""
Framework scaffolder.

If the configured framework path is empty (or missing the base plumbing), this
creates a complete, runnable Selenium-Cucumber framework for plain JDK
(javac + java, no Maven):

    <framework>/
      libs/                      <- jars (populate with scripts/get-libs)
      src/main/java/
        core/DriverFactory.java      Edge driver (live by default), -D flags
        core/ConfigReader.java       environment config
        core/LocatorRepository.java  central repo client + self-healing hook
      src/test/java/
        stepdefinitions/Hooks.java   before/after, screenshots on failure
      src/test/resources/
        features/                    generated .feature files land here
        config/SIT.properties        per-environment URLs
      run.bat / run.sh               manual one-command execution

Generated artifacts (features, step defs, page objects) are then written into
this structure by the generation engine after approval.
"""
